title: Learning Estonian
description:
Learn Estonian from a native speaker

Estonian language is considered one of the most difficult Latin based alphabet ones because:
1\ It has 14 cases
2\ of 4 special letters: ä, ö, ü and õ
3\ There are short, long and extended vocals
